Depends: proot, tar, axel, nethunter-cli
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://wpscan.com/
Description: WordPress Security Scanner
 WPScan is a black box WordPress security scanner used to test
 the security of WordPress websites by checking for vulnerabilities,
 weak passwords, and misconfigurations.
